title: Travel and Babble
description:
In this episode, Jessi and Stew are joined by Addie Mackay who is also a stylist and educator at JZ Styles Co. They talk about their favorite travel memories and also talk travel hacks they have found helpful over the years. This episode will have you dying with the things that get revealed!
